description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;CCHP is a partnership led by Sirona care &amp; health CIC working with Avon &amp; Wiltshire Partnership Mental Health NHS Trust (AWP), University Hospital Bristol NHS Foundation Trust (UHB), Barnardo’s and Off The Record as partners. Together we provide all of the community child health and child and adolescent mental health services for Bristol, North Somerset and South Gloucestershire. The service is called the Community Children’s Health Partnership (CCHP).&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Service user participation is an important part of our service and we are keen to involve children and young people to help us improve the services we offer.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We have over 800 staff in CCHP including:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Community Paediatricians&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Children’s Therapists&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Health Visitors&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;School Health Nurses&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Children’s Mental Health Teams&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We also provide a range of more specialised children’s mental health services and services for children with disabilities.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The School Age Speech and Language Therapy team provide support to children and young people attending mainstream and secondary schools, at a universal, targeted and specialist level.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Owing to internal promotion we have a part time (26.25hpw) fixed term vacancy in our Bristol Team, based in Eastgate Hub.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post involves working within the designated school age team, being the ‘link’ therapist for a designated group of schools, providing advice and guidance to schools at a universal and targeted level, and assessment and intervention of children and young people referred into the service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To view the role in more detail please see the Job Description, for further queries please contact the recruitment team - sirona.recruitment@nhs.net.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
